    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263290/extras/9b98fb7f115cb7c3f970bccd1f6c94de.poster.avif?t=1678580639\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263290/extras/9b98fb7f115cb7c3f970bccd1f6c94de.webm?t=1678580639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263290/extras/9b98fb7f115cb7c3f970bccd1f6c94de.mp4?t=1678580639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In the distant future, calamity descends from the heavens.  A meteor lands off the coast and sends the local ecosystem wild.  You take the role of John Sheider, typical Ex-Secret Agent and Highschool Science Teacher.  It's your job to seek out research material and investigate the phenomenon, by diving deep beneath the waves.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263290/extras/95ccb53d1b7d16ce75ac59dd1c1081a0.poster.avif?t=1678580639\" width=616 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263290/extras/95ccb53d1b7d16ce75ac59dd1c1081a0.webm?t=1678580639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263290/extras/95ccb53d1b7d16ce75ac59dd1c1081a0.mp4?t=1678580639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore the coast, searching for new locations in a dynamic world, but take care... you are not alone.  Something is affecting the local marine-life, and citizens are going missing.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263290/extras/6badce92c3a6753f819c728ce5bedfae.poster.avif?t=1678580639\" width=616 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263290/extras/6badce92c3a6753f819c728ce5bedfae.webm?t=1678580639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263290/extras/6badce92c3a6753f819c728ce5bedfae.mp4?t=1678580639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You're not alone however.  Captain Shaw, the Charter boat captain will lend you his nautical know how, and Miss Dreyfuss will lend you her mechanical expertise.  Fight in the air, on reel, and sea.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263290/extras/9b573a8d0e39dbb49733f89d93e75b01.poster.avif?t=1678580639\" width=616 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263290/extras/9b573a8d0e39dbb49733f89d93e75b01.webm?t=1678580639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263290/extras/9b573a8d0e39dbb49733f89d93e75b01.mp4?t=1678580639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Accessibility Options:</strong><br>-Auto-fire and Auto-movement settings allow MOUSE-ONLY gameplay with minimal button inputs.<br>-Full Keybinding/Remapping.<br>-Edit Cursor colors, along with important overlays.<br>-Controller support, and thumbstick deadzone settings.<br>-Dyslexic friendly font, with OpenDyslexic.<br><br>This game is planned for full release in the 1st Quarter of 2023.  You can follow along with the development @Coleowing on Twitter, Youtube, Twitch, Tiktok, or Instagram.",
